Solving the impurity model and computing the normal and anomalous Green's functions $G=-\left\langle T{c}\left(\tau\right){c}^{\dagger}\right\rangle $
and $F=-\left\langle T{c}^{\dagger}\left(\tau\right){c}^{\dagger}\right\rangle $,
