F\left(i\omega_{n}\right) & -G\left(i\omega_{n}\right)^{\star}
\end{array}\right)
\end{eqnarray}
and analogously for the two components of the ``Weiss field", which coincide with the non-interacting Green's functions of (\ref{eq:SC_imp_Ham}).
